songs.title: Meghan Interlude
songs.lyrics:
[Skit]
"If you feel those things about me, why can't you be with me?"

[Intro]
Manchester girl, London girl
Thanks for vibin’ with me
Spending time here with me
But I got things to do, at home
Nobody wants to be alone (turn it up a little bit)

[Verse 1]
Just let me leave baby (yeah)
I want the (?) baby
You can't see, I'm your Jodeci baby
(?) baby, from the underground baby
That’s that uptown, that's that
West-side, best-side, that's that
Fuck the rest side

[Hook]
I'm still going, going, running, running, coming
There's no fun in always runnin' (?) (yeah, yeah)
Open your legs, let me see your body (body)
Give me the rest and show me you're bout it (act like you want me)
Yeah

[Bridge] (x2)
Shawty you got it good, shawty you got it
Shawty you got it good, shawty you got it
Shawty you got it good, shawty you got it

[Hook]
I'm still going, going, running, running, coming
There’s no fun in always (?) (yeah, yeah)
Open your legs, let me to your body (body)
Give me the rest and show me you’re bout it (act like you want me)
Yeah
